### BeatInfo Data Structure

```python
@dataclass
class BeatInfo:
    is_beat: bool              # True if beat detected this frame
    beat_type: str             # "kick", "snare", "hihat", "none"
    bpm: float                 # Current BPM estimate
    phase: float               # 0-1 phase within beat (0 = downbeat)
    confidence: float          # 0-1 confidence in detection
    onset_strength: float      # Raw onset detection value
    time_since_last_beat: float # Seconds
```

