## What It Does NOT Do

- ❌ Does **not** perform full music transcription (note-level)
- ❌ Does **not** do key or chord detection (separate module)
- ❌ Does **not** handle polyrhythms or complex meters (assumes 4/4)
- ❌ Does **not** store beat history long-term (ephemeral)
- ❌ Does **not** provide MIDI output (use MIDIController)
- ❌ Does **not** do tempo-synced effects (use LFO modules)

