## Success Criteria

### Must Pass (All Required)

- [ ] FPS ≥ 58 when beat detector active
- [ ] All unit tests pass (≥80% coverage)
- [ ] BPM estimation within ±5 BPM of ground truth on 90% of test tracks
- [ ] Beat detection precision > 85% (few false positives)
- [ ] Beat detection recall > 90% (few missed beats)
- [ ] Phase accuracy: < 10ms jitter
- [ ] Thread-safe: no race conditions in `get_beat_info()`
- [ ] Works with both `sounddevice` and `pyaudio` backends

### Should Pass (Best Effort)

- [ ] Classification accuracy > 80% (kick/snare/hihat)
- [ ] Handles tempo changes within 2 seconds
- [ ] Supports BPM range 60-200 (extended to 40-240 if possible)
- [ ] Beat tracking across song transitions (DJ mix)
- [ ] Low-latency mode (< 10ms) for live performance

