## Risks & Mitigations

| Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|------------|--------|------------|
| False positives on transients | Medium | Medium | Tune threshold, use multiple algorithms |
| BPM drift over time | Medium | High | Running average, reset on downbeat |
| Genre-specific performance | High | Medium | Train on diverse dataset, adaptive params |
| Latency too high | Low | Medium | Optimize FFT, use overlap-add |
| Thread contention | Low | Medium | Lock-free reads, double-buffering |

